<plot>"Anniversary Present" is a short comedy about marital dysfunction. The film begins with matrimony but quickly leads into the decline of a young couple's union and a sudden fit of jealousy that results in the complete and utter destruction of their brand new red sports car. Juxtaposing metal crushing intensity with the high stakes of love, "Anniversary Present" will give insight into what makes the modern marriage keep ticking.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?041782</url></doc>
